<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:12:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国称2024年国防开支将增长7.2%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-says-2024-defence-spending-to-rise-7-2/articleshow/108218645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-says-2024-defence-spending-to-rise-7-2/articleshow/108218645.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国空军雇员被指控在在线约会网站上分享机密信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-air-force-employee-accused-of-sharing-classified-information-on-online-dating-website/articleshow/108218543.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218543.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国司法部周一表示，美国空军雇员大卫·富兰克林·斯莱特因与他在外国在线约会平台上认识的一名女子泄露机密国防信息而被捕。斯莱特于周五在内布拉斯加州因三项联邦起诉书被拘留，预计将于周二首次出庭。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-air-force-employee-accused-of-sharing-classified-information-on-online-dating-website/articleshow/108218543.cms</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿州和爱达荷州分别发生雪崩，造成 2 名雪地摩托司机丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-snowmobilers-killed-in-separate-avalanches-in-washington-and-idaho/articleshow/108218982.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218982.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;华盛顿州和爱达荷州分别发生雪崩，两名雪地摩托车手丧生。据西北雪崩中心称，在华盛顿州亚基马，达兰德山附近的喀斯喀特山脉中，骑手引发了滑坡。在爱达荷州，一名雪地摩托车手在塞尔扣克山脉南部丧生。已故的雪地摩托车手被确认为来自爱达荷州桑德波因特的兰斯·吉德利 (Lance J. Gidley)。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-snowmobilers-killed-in-separate-avalanches-in-washington-and-idaho/articleshow/108218982.cms</guid></item><item><title>被指控的五角大楼泄密者认罪，面临近 17 年监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accused-pentagon-leaker-pleads-guilty-faces-almost-17-years-jail/articleshow/108218541.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218541.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;这名美国飞行员被指控在网上发布大量五角大楼高度机密文件，周一在联邦法院认罪。作为谈判协议的一部分，他同意被判处约 17 年监禁，作为交换，检察官同意撤销更严厉的间谍指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:30:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accused-pentagon-leaker-pleads-guilty-faces-almost-17-years-jail/articleshow/108218541.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列和联合国贸易指控“恐怖主义”和酷刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-un-trade-allegations-of-terrorism-torture/articleshow/108218522.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218522.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于处理 10 月 7 日袭击期间哈马斯武装分子性侵犯指控的问题引发紧张局势，以色列于周一召回了驻联合国大使。以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹因争端升级而被召回进行磋商，他表示，“联合国花了五个月的时间才最终承认 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀期间犯下的性犯罪行为。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-un-trade-allegations-of-terrorism-torture/articleshow/108218522.cms</guid></item><item><title>“有理由相信”哈马斯袭击期间发生的强奸事件：联合国报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/grounds-to-believe-rapes-committed-during-hamas-attacks-un-report/articleshow/108218422.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218422.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国周一发布的一份报告称，有“合理的理由相信”哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列期间发生了强奸事件，随后被劫持到加沙的人质也遭到强奸。报告称：“调查小组发现，有合理的理由相信，10 月 7 日袭击期间，多个地点发生了与冲突有关的性暴力，包括强奸和轮奸。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/grounds-to-believe-rapes-committed-during-hamas-attacks-un-report/articleshow/108218422.cms</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处负责人警告全球和平与安全受到严重影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-chief-warns-of-serious-implications-for-global-peace-security/articleshow/108218368.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108218368.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-chief-warns-of-serious-implications-for-global-peace-security/articleshow/108218368.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在与内塔尼亚胡竞争对手的会谈中对加沙局势表示“深切关注”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-vp-kamala-harris-expresses-deep-concerns-over-gaza-situation-in-talks-with-netanyahu-rival/articleshow/108217004.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108217004.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周一在与以色列战时内阁成员、总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的头号竞争对手本尼·甘茨的会谈中对加沙平民面临的局势表示“深切关注”。甘茨加入了 10 月 7 日后组建的五人战时内阁，旨在促进该国的团结。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 22:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-vp-kamala-harris-expresses-deep-concerns-over-gaza-situation-in-talks-with-netanyahu-rival/articleshow/108217004.cms</guid></item><item><title>首先，法国将堕胎列为宪法权利</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/in-a-first-france-makes-abortion-a-constitutional-right/articleshow/108216087.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216087.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:59:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/in-a-first-france-makes-abortion-a-constitutional-right/articleshow/108216087.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国向马尔代夫提供无偿军事援助；签署协议以加强双边关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-to-provide-free-military-assistance-to-maldives-inks-agreement-to-bolster-bilateral-ties/articleshow/108216080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国和马尔代夫签署了防务合作协议，中国提供无偿军事援助以加强双边关系。该协议由马尔代夫国防部长穆罕默德·加桑·穆蒙和中国少将张宝群签署。这一事态发展是在马尔代夫为第一批印度军事人员撤出该国设定最后期限之后发生的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:54:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-to-provide-free-military-assistance-to-maldives-inks-agreement-to-bolster-bilateral-ties/articleshow/108216080.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国出人意料地取消总理年度新闻发布会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-scraps-premiers-annual-news-conference-in-surprise-move/articleshow/108216071.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216071.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国总理将不再在年度全国人大会议后举行新闻发布会。这一决定反映了中国日益增加的信息不透明度和习近平权力的巩固。政府对透明度和营造友好商业环境的承诺遭到破坏。与下级官员的问答环节将取代新闻发布会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-scraps-premiers-annual-news-conference-in-surprise-move/articleshow/108216071.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国和俄罗斯因乌克兰导弹音频泄露发生争执</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-and-russia-spar-over-a-leaked-audio-on-missiles-for-ukraine-berlin-promises-to-investigate/articleshow/108216041.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216041.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国政府否认了有关俄罗斯公布德国高级军官泄露的谈话内容暗示柏林正在准备对俄罗斯开战的指控。虽然德国当局没有质疑录音的真实性，但德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，将这些武器运送到乌克兰并不是一种选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-and-russia-spar-over-a-leaked-audio-on-missiles-for-ukraine-berlin-promises-to-investigate/articleshow/108216041.cms</guid></item><item><title>苹果在 Spotify 案中被欧盟罚款 20 亿美元，将上诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/apple-hit-with-2-billion-eu-antitrust-fine-in-spotify-case-will-appeal/articleshow/108215933.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108215933.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟委员会因不公平的交易条件以及阻止 Spotify 向用户告知 App Store 之外的支付选项而对苹果公司处以 18.4 亿欧元的罚款。苹果计划对这一决定提出质疑，并寻求解决另一项欧盟反垄断调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/apple-hit-with-2-billion-eu-antitrust-fine-in-spotify-case-will-appeal/articleshow/108215933.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国立法者投票将堕胎纳入宪法权利</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/french-lawmakers-votes-to-make-abortion-constitutional-right/articleshow/108214688.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214688.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国议会周一投票将堕胎权纳入该国宪法，使其成为第一个在基本法中为终止妊娠提供明确保护的国家。聚集在凡尔赛宫的议会下院和上院轻松获得了这一变革所需的五分之三多数，其中 72 名议员投了反对票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/french-lawmakers-votes-to-make-abortion-constitutional-right/articleshow/108214688.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列罢工导致三名黎巴嫩真主党相关部队救援人员死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-strike-kills-three-lebanese-rescue-workers-from-hezbollah-linked-force/articleshow/108214986.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214986.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列在黎巴嫩南部的一次袭击造成三名真主党紧急救援人员死亡。政府和 Al-Hayaa 救援部队证实了这起杀戮事件，使自 10 月以来在以色列袭击中丧生的紧急救援人员总数达到七人。一月份的另一次罢工导致两名急救人员死亡。这场冲突是2006年战争以来最严重的一次，引发了人们对更大规模对抗的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:40:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-strike-kills-three-lebanese-rescue-workers-from-hezbollah-linked-force/articleshow/108214986.cms</guid></item><item><title>白宫称美国呼吁结束海地暴力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-calls-for-end-to-haiti-violence-white-house-says/articleshow/108215205.cms</link><description>白宫周一表示，美国敦促海地所有行为者停止暴力，并将海地人民放在第一位。白宫发言人约翰·柯比表示，白宫正在密切关注海地局势。周末暴力升级，又有 15,000 人逃离战火，武装人员从海地最大的监狱冲走了数千名囚犯。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-calls-for-end-to-haiti-violence-white-house-says/articleshow/108215205.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普集团前首席财务官承认伪证罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/former-trump-organization-cfo-pleads-guilty-to-perjury/articleshow/108215235.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108215235.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;检察官周一表示，唐纳德·特朗普组织的前财务总监因提供与前总统民事欺诈审判有关的虚假信息而承认作伪证。 76 岁的艾伦·韦塞尔伯格 (Allen Weisselberg) 在 2005 年至 2021 年期间担任前总统特朗普房地产和娱乐集团的首席财务官。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/former-trump-organization-cfo-pleads-guilty-to-perjury/articleshow/108215235.cms</guid></item><item><title>冈比亚议会考虑取消女性生殖器切割禁令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gambian-parliament-mulls-lifting-ban-on-female-genital-mutilation/articleshow/108215312.cms</link><description>冈比亚议会周一开始审查一项备受争议的法案，该法案旨在取消自 2015 年以来生效的女性生殖器切割禁令。几个月来，这个问题在冈比亚人中产生了分歧，数十名示威者聚集在议会内外，寻求取消该禁令。禁令。但一些民间社会团体敦促政府立场坚定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:32:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gambian-parliament-mulls-lifting-ban-on-female-genital-mutilation/articleshow/108215312.cms</guid></item><item><title>超过十分之六的美国成年人怀疑拜登第二任期的心理能力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/more-than-6-in-10-us-adults-doubts-bidens-mental-capability-for-second-term/articleshow/108214035.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214035.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近的一项调查显示，越来越多的美国成年人因拜登的年龄而对他有效履行职责的能力产生怀疑。约60%的受访者对拜登的心理能力缺乏信心，较今年早些时候略有上升。即将到来的选举被视为对世界上最艰巨工作的考验，两位候选人都已超过退休年龄。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/more-than-6-in-10-us-adults-doubts-bidens-mental-capability-for-second-term/articleshow/108214035.cms</guid></item><item><title>SC 消除了特朗普入主白宫的巨大障碍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/supreme-court-removes-giant-hurdle-from-trumps-path-to-white-house/articleshow/108214032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国最高法院一致驳回了州法院的一项裁决，为唐纳德·特朗普的总统竞选扫清了道路。该裁决推翻了有关叛乱的指控，这些指控可能阻止他出现在选票上。法院的裁决巩固了特朗普获得共和党提名的道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:17:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/supreme-court-removes-giant-hurdle-from-trumps-path-to-white-house/articleshow/108214032.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>